            <specpara>
                <note>
                    <para>Before installation, make sure the sensor tip is free of metal chips. To adjust sensor
                        clearance, turn sensor in clockwise until contact is made on a tailshaft gear tooth. Back out
                        one full turn and tighten the locknut.
                    </para>
